Key Features:
Search: by title, author, subject, ISBN, or all.
Filters: language, year range, favorites.
Sorting: relevance, year (asc/desc), editions.
Pagination: customizable results per page.
Favorites: toggle, persist in localStorage, filter to show only favorites.
Debounced Input: reduces unnecessary API calls.
Details Modal: shows description, subjects, top editions.
Keyboard Shortcuts: / to focus search, f to toggle favorites.
UI: Responsive grid layout, cover images, Tailwind CSS styling.
Data Flow:
Search term → Build API query → Fetch results → Client-side filtering/sorting → Display results → Modal shows detailed info.
